1 is a tremendous loss to his family, the Shreveport City Marshal's Office, and the entire
2 community he so faithfully served; and
3 WHEREAS, his legacy will live on through the lives he touched, the youth he
4 mentored, the family he loved, and the community he served with honor and distinction.
5 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Louisiana of Legislature
6 does hereby honor the life and legacy of Assistant Chief City Marshal Kirby Shawn Dawson
7 and extends heartfelt condolences to his wife, children, family, colleagues, and all who
8 mourn his passing.
9 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
10 family of Assistant Chief City Marshal, Kirby Shawn Dawson as an expression of our
11 deepest sympathy and appreciation for his life of service.
